import React from 'react'
import { Router, Switch, Route } from 'react-router'
import { history } from '../History'

import Login from '../Pages/Login'
import Registro from '../Pages/Registro'
import Home from '../Pages/Home'
import NotFound from '../Components/NotFound'
import Usuario from '../Components/UsuarioForms'
import Filmes from '../Components/FilmeForms'
import Genero from '../Components/GeneroForms'

const Routes = () => (
    <Router history={ history } >
        <Switch>
            <Route component= { Login } exact path ="/login/"/>
            <Route component= { Registro } exact path ="/Registro/"/>
            <Route component= { Home } exact path = "/Home/"/>

            <Route component= { Usuario } exact path ="/Usuario/"/>
            <Route component= { Filmes } exact path ="/Filmes/"/>
            <Route component= { Genero } exact path ="/Genero/"/>

            <Route component= { Genero } exact path ="/Genero/"/>

            <Route/>
        </Switch>
    </Router>
)

export default Routes
